<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>회원가입 | DAMORE</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f3ef;
      color: #111;
    }
    .wrap {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 460px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 36px 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 34px;
    }
    p {
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    input {
      width: 100%;
      height: 52px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      outline: none;
    }
    button {
      width: 100%;
      height: 54px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #111;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .links {
      margin-top: 18px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .links a {
      color: #111;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .home-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>회원가입</h1>
      <p>DAMORE 회원가입</p>

      <form method="POST" action="/register">
        <label>이름</label>
        <input type="text" name="name" required />

        <label>이메일</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" required />

        <label>비밀번호</label>
        <input type="password" name="password" required />

        <label>비밀번호 확인</label>
        <input type="password" name="passwordConfirm" required />

        <button type="submit">회원가입</button>
      </form>

      <div class="links">
        이미 회원이면 <a href="/login">로그인</a>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="home-link">← 메인으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>